Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:43.65,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(800,500)}Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:41.80,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bro, it's difficult to dig here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.95,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:45.34,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,{\an8}These islands are mostly just tree roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:48.21,Main,Not Zoro,0,0,0,,Please forgive us!  Don't bury us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.82,Main,Not Sanji,0,0,0,,We'll do whatever you want, just don't kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:54.70,Main,Not Franky,0,0,0,,The captain forced us into it!  That damn Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:59.48,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,As soon as we'd joined the crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:03.20,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,we planned on taking out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.04,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,every last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:12.54,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,of the infamous Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.17,Main,Not Zoro,0,0,0,,Drip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.36,Main,Not Franky,0,0,0,,Hey, please stop it!  He'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.63,Main,Not Franky,0,0,0,,You've got Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.33,Main,Not Sogeking,0,0,0,,S-Stop, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.88,Main,Not Sogeking,0,0,0,,What's with him?!  Is he a Logi{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.28,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:39.54,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,I assumed that your faces and physiques had changed, it'd been 2 years after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:41.62,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,But the pirate, Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.27,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,was just a nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.46,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,A filthy impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:48.78,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Do you think God will forgive this, Coribou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.31,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Dig!  Dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.48,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Indeed, my friends!  Let's bury 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.91,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.68,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,I will bury these imbeciles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.59,Main,Not Nami,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:07.99,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,However, I've seen the real Straw Hat Luffy\Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:13.93,Captions,Sign,0,0,180,,{\fad(800,500)}The former rendezvous point of the Fake Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:14.03,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,{\an8}As I said, there was nothing we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:17.58,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,We were up against the Dark King Rayleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:21.34,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,He could fight off uncle Kizaru.\NWhat could we have done against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:26.38,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,The only ones that escaped from the plaza were the Caribou brothers with their crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.95,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,and a few members of the fake Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.95,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,We captured everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:36.81,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,but the real Straw Hat Pirates dealt heavy damage\Nto the 2 Pacifista that I brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:41.00,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,They are the same prototypes that cornered them 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.83,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,Of course, the Pacifistas' strength can't have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.30,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,The change must have been in those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:51.15,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,During their 2-year absence,\Nthey've grown incredibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:57.52,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,Send word to Navy HQ in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.88,Main,Sentoumaru,0,0,0,,The Straw Hat Pirates have completely recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.28,Main,Shakki,0,0,0,,They're gone in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:13.46,Main,Shakki,0,0,0,,Monkey-chan and the rest sure have become tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.08,Main,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.63,Main,Shakki,0,0,0,,Of course.  I am a fan, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:20.97,Main,Shakki,0,0,0,,Are you remembering something, Ray-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:25.27,Main,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.65,Flashbacks,Roger,0,0,0,,Hey!  That's a nice ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:31.73,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,It's a stolen ship.\NMy house burned down, so I'm living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.96,Flashbacks,Roger,0,0,0,,I see.  What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.35,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,It's Rayleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:41.32,Flashbacks,Roger,0,0,0,,I'm Roger!  Our meeting here is destiny, Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.76,Flashbacks,Roger,0,0,0,,Wanna come with me and turn the world on its head?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.57,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,The world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.11,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.14,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:58.40,Main,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,Maybe there are no coincidences in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:01.74,Main,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,It's possible that everything happens for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:06.06,Main,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,Fate works in mysterious ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:13.47,Main,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, Luffy has become a man\Nworthy to wear that hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.25,Main,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,I suppose it might not be too bad, living a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:20.60,Captions,Sign,0,0,180,,{\fad(500,0)}The waters around the Sabaody Archipelago - Beneath the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.60,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\an8}The surface is already so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:26.21,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What a sight!  We don't get a view this wide\Nin the submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.55,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We're sinking faster and faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.05,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Is the water really not gonna come in?  I'm worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.79,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It feels like we're drifting away from the human world!  I'm tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:40.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A-Are we gonna be able to return to the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.51,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Not that I'm scared or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The ocean sure is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.68,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Look at this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.39,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Trees!  No, roots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:59.54,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Yeah... Now that I think about it, the\NSabaody Archipelago is one giant mangrove, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.99,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The splendor of nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.05,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I've already seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.88,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, 'cause you got on the wrong ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.27,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shut up!  Let us be in awe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.74,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe that the roots\Nstretch all the way to the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.61,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,They're so big, I'm speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:19.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper...\NThere's something behind those trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.94,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's humongous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:27.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!  An adventure beneath the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I think I can catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:37.05,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,There are some tasty looking fish over here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.68,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.45,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What if the soap bubble breaks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.45,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you if you do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:49.17,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Nami-san, before these two do something else stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:50.96,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,could you tell us how this coating works?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.10,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I guess so, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.67,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Rayleigh-san gave me some notes, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.74,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,So, let me explain it to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.84,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,She moved!  A real life beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.39,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.69,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's breaking!  Breaking!  Breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.34,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Just how far can you be propelled by a nosebleed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.78,Main,Them,0,0,0,,Sanji got thrown into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.39,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The ocean!  My strength is fading...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.21,Main,Usopp & Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.89,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What happened to you, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:28.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's like you've developed\Na crippling weakness to women!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.69,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.56,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:36.51,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What could have happened these last 2 years,\Nto turn the lady-loving Sanji-san into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:40.43,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,At this rate, once he meets the mermaids he was longing to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:43.16,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,he might die from blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.50,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We'll have to get\Na blood transfusion for him on Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.75,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I wonder if fishmen and mermen have the same blood types as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.84,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,So basically, like we just saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:59.89,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,the soap-bubble surrounding this ship has the same properties as the ones on the Sabaody Archipelago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.24,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Don't just calmly continue your analysis of soap-bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.00,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.13,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Fundamentally, they're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:09.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,They'll stretch to a certain extent,\Nand after that, you'll pierce through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.15,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,In a worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:16.17,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,if we're attacked by sea monsters, we can fire a cannonball at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.00,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,The bubble won't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:21.75,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Then what would it take for it to break?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:26.40,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,As you'd expect, it won't hold if\Na large number of holes are opened at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:31.49,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,For example, if a sea monster or Sea King\Nbites the ship, we're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.22,Main,Usopp and Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look out, behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.01,Main,Usopp and Chopper,0,0,0,,A fight... We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:43.44,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,If we crash into rocks or a trench and\Nthe ship itself takes damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:47.35,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,then fractures in the mast or hull\Ncould cause the bubble to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.50,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,So we have to avoid that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:53.20,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Basically, we have to look out for\Nsea creatures and other obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:57.03,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,As long as we don't do anything stupid in here,\Nthere's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.57,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I see!  It's stronger than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:05.69,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,However, of all the ships that set off for Fishman Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.49,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,70% are destroyed.  Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.60,Main,Usopp & Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's gonna happen to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:16.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If I use my Gatling on them,\NI'm sure I can catch all of those fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:20.41,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Then how about we compete\Nto see who can catch the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:24.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weren't you listening to what Nami said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.45,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't open a bunch of holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna beat the crap out of you two!\NNever do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.92,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:37.33,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hachi said he'd lead us to Fishman Island,\Nso I didn't think it'd be this dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:42.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I've got tons of lunch boxes.\NAnd since Sanji's knocked out right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Everyone!  Let's have some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.03,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Yay!  My stomach's rumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.95,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My bones are rumbling as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.96,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Nami, will the ship be safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:58.25,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Well, right now we're just riding a large ocean current, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:03.68,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,See, there's something I need to tell all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.81,Main,They,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your hidden robotic functions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.08,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,No, sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.15,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am afraid that is incorrect, robo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.68,Main,They,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa, awesome!  Robot-language!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:18.79,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The truth is, Hachi had planned to\Ncome and guide us across the ocean floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.40,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,but I heard he suffered major injuries on Sabaody,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.60,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,and is now recovering on Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.60,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,His reason is the same as Duval's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:32.06,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,He fought to protect the Thousand Sunny, which had been left behind on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:36.00,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,About a year ago, the Navy found out\Nwhere the Sunny was docked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:40.08,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,In the fierce battle that followed,\Nboth of them were forced to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:44.82,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Huh?  Then how'd the ship last until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.09,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Because there was one more warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:53.22,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The very same man who\Nscattered us 2 years ago, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:59.98,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,A member of the Seven Royal Warlords of the Sea, and a great man, Bartholomew Kuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.56,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,A few days ago, when I arrived at the Sunny,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:06.61,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.11,Flashbacks,Kuma,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.81,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Damn you!  What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:17.26,Flashbacks,Kuma,0,0,0,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The Sunny didn't have a single scratch on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.33,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,And when I spoke to Rayleigh afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.80,Flashbacks,Kuma,0,0,0,,I am an officer in the Revolutionary Army. {Copy-paste from 507}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.34,Flashbacks,Kuma,0,0,0,,Because of this,\NI wish to let this crew escape. {End copy-paste from 507}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:38.06,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you figured it out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:41.35,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,He saved our lives back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:48.03,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,And after we vanished from the island, Kuma-san visited Rayleigh and said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:52.59,Flashbacks,Kuma,0,0,0,,The time I have left... is running out. {Copy-paste from 507.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:55.49,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I don't know what they were holding over him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:13:00.97,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,but he allowed the Navy to experiment on his body,\Nand they slowly turned him into a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.13,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Shortly before the great war,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:07.10,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,he agreed to undergo a modification that would remove his personality completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:14.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,But there's no way he could've known what we'd do after we were scattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:17.89,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,And yet he waited for us by the ship?  Even though he'd lost his personality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.82,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It seems that while he was with the surgeon, Doctor Vegapunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:26.80,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,he got a promise that a certain mission would be programmed into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:33.69,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Guard the ship until\Na member of the Straw Hat Pirates returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:37.33,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So, for two years he's been waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:43.17,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Despite being a human weapon without memories, he's been obeying the orders from his past self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.98,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,His methods are completely messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.74,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Why would he go that far for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.54,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,He's with the Revolutionary Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:55.82,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,The only explanation I can think of\Nis that Luffy's dad is their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.20,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I don't really know much about my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:01.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But I guess that bear-like guy was a good guy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.13,Thoughts,Robin,0,0,0,,Kuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.87,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Well, the fact remains that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:13.84,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,he was the one who allowed us to\Nsurvive these 2 years and make them worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:19.06,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Though by now, there's no way for us to ask him why he did what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:22.32,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Just keep this fact stored in your hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:28.05,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This crew is indebted to Bartholomew Kuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:34.42,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,But even if we meet him again, Kuma has become nothing more than a heartless human weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:37.57,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to him, but this raises a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.22,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I hope we'll be able to find out Kuma's true intentions one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That is all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.99,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Oh, Sanji, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:46.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Have a lunch box!  It's from the Island of Women!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.00,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,The Island of Women...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.84,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Why should I be grateful to Kuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.92,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea where I've been for 2 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:59.67,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What kind of training did you do on that all-women island of dreams, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:03.34,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Now, now, now, Sanji-san.\NShall we sing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.85,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Don't try to comfort me!\NYou're making me feel pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.34,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Bro!  There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.85,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Ahead!  The Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:13.41,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,I can see that, you dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.77,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,This time I'll get to board that ship, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I wonder how far we've sunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:23.87,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,There isn't much light this far down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:28.93,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,We already passed through the sunlight level and\Nnow we're nearing the end of the twilight level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.08,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,We must be more than\Na kilometer down by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:36.04,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It's so quiet.\NThis feels completely different to the submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.59,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It's almost like we're flying through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,A whale!  It's a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.16,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Laboon?  Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.92,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,No, that's old man Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.47,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I see something at 6 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.21,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A sea monster?  No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.57,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Are you ready, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:54.05,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Yeah, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.37,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!  Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:58.27,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Our goal is right before our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.65,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,We could destroy their ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.39,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,and send the wreckage straight to the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:09.56,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,But that's no good.\NIf we did that, no one would know who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.78,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,We'll take their heads\Nand bring them back to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:17.40,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,That's how we'll sing out to the world,\N"Caribou is here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.46,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.31,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,They'll be completely unprepared for a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:25.82,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,This is a perfect sneak attack!\NDon't mess this up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.23,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.30,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Aye!  Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.13,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A shadow that looks like a ship is approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.25,Main,Sanji & Zoro,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:34.92,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,A ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.47,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's headed straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.48,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.78,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.67,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,They're ramming our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:50.07,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Get away!  The bubble will break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.69,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,No way!  They're trying to break into our soap bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:55.81,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.83,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Good job, sea cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.93,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.17,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Are they planning to board our ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.27,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sea cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.88,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Wait! Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.86,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Alright! Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.08,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.72,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Hey, Mohmoo! {Gil: Timing appeared one frame early. Hope I changed it correctly.} {Yup, it's good now -FAb}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.92,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're Mohmoo from Arlong's crew, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.82,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.93,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!  Haven't we seen this guy before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.26,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.68,Flashbacks,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.92,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rubber Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.57,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Let's board their ship, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.28,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.15,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone's coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:45.66,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Are you ready, men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.92,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:54.89,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,While these guys... stand there... dumbfounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:58.43,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,every last one of 'em... will be slaughtered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.24,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.31,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:05.71,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Men!  Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:11.34,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.89,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,What's wrong, sea cow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:14.25,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this, sea cow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:17.52,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,How can this be?!\NCaptain Caribou was left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.77,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.82,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Now... How about we give them a little greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:28.03,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Fire the Gatling gun at 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:34.57,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Kill every last member... of the Straw Hat Crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.71,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:47.68,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,P-Please, don't throw me into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:48.80,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,That's all I ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.21,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:54.03,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,You mustn't take another's life so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.32,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,God! { def: i'm going with consistency here and sticking with "God" (unless we get a confirmed plural translation).  it works with his crusaderish insignia as well. }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.13,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,God is watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:57.95,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:05.23,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Don't get cheeky with me!  Who was just talking about slaughter and Gatling guns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.96,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.77,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,You're the captain of that pirate ship, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.97,Thoughts,Caribou,0,0,0,,Hm?!  Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:16.89,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Oh, you're mistaken!  I'm not the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.54,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,I was, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:22.56,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,I was just being used as their slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.05,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm sick of being on that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.56,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!  Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.05,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Can you let me stay on your ship for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.22,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Please!  I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:34.75,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You know, I kinda feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:37.57,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!  He's obviously lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.90,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!  It was all a lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.46,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.10,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What was with the sea cow that was pulling the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.83,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:51.60,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,What have we here?  Quite a cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.41,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,You're the Cat Burglar, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:59.28,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Don't you dare look at our gorgeous navigator\Nwith those vulgar eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:03.26,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Nami-san, it's gonna be fine... now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:07.52,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That's getting really annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:11.84,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,It's just a sea monster that we caught in these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:18.09,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Using creatures like that to pull your ship is how professionals travel underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.27,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.96,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,Stop!  Stop, sea cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.18,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,What happened, sea cow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:29.18,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Bro!  I'm gonna save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I wonder if there are any sea monsters around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:35.88,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Luffy.  What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:40.59,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We'll start rehabilitating you with photos\Nsince they don't have as much of an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.06,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:45.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Are we going in a different direction\Nfrom the one the Log Pose is pointing in? {zzz}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.90,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Yes, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:50.87,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We should move southwest of the compass needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:54.62,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But going directly toward the island would be faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:21:00.28,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Apparently, if you follow the needle directly,\Nyou'll get caught up in the ocean currents,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,and crash into an underwater mountain or volcano\Nbefore reaching your destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.42,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What?!  A volcano?!  The ocean floor is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:12.22,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,But I thought that all the currents of the Grand Line\Nare completely out of whack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:14.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Is there really a current that {\i1}isn't{\i0} going to cause us problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:16.76,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Yeah, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:21.83,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Everyone!  It's gonna get cold soon.  You'd better put on a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:25.98,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,True, my skin is starting to get goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.65,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Ah!  Though I{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.41,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You're all bones, so you don't have skin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:35.26,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,We're going somewhere cold?\NAren't we headed for the ocean floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:38.82,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Of course the water at the ocean floor is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:42.40,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Even in a bath, the water's warmer at the top\Nand colder on the bottom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:48.11,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Oh, right.  So if it's the same for the sea,\Nthe water down deep is colder than surface water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:51.13,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Temperature isn't the only thing that's different...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:54.12,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Will you get over it already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.60,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,In the deeper parts of the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:02.89,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,there are giant currents known as "deep currents"\Nthat you usually can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.89,0:22:07.94,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,They are completely different from\Nthe surface currents we've been riding so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:10.96,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,There are currents beneath the currents?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:12.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You sure are knowledgeable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:15.85,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Only because I have lived for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:19.71,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The currents all have to connect somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:22.90,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,They flow from the east or the west\Nand then meet up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.02,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Plunging downward and surging back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:28.73,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's almost like an enormous dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:33.18,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Apparently the deep currents flow very slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:35.81,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,They say that once water goes down to the ocean floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.97,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,it can take 2,000 years\Nbefore it returns to a level that sees the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:43.58,Main,Trio,0,0,0,,{\i1}2,000 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:49.20,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Indeed.  Furthermore, there are countless legends...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:52.81,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,about those dark, unknown sea currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:57.96,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Monsters, curses, and souls of the damned!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:01.07,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaaaaat?!  There are ghosts in the deep seas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:03.32,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!  There are?!  Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:04.63,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:06.71,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Ghosts, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:08.36,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I don't know about all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:13.84,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,but we're gonna use the downflow to dive\Nfrom the surface currents to the deep currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:17.94,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,By doing that, we'll be able to reach the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:21.57,Main,Four,0,0,0,,So it's a mysterious sea current.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:24.20,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't understand any of that, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.89,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Shall we sing a song, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:27.64,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Nami, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:28.66,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:30.56,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The mysterious sea current?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:33.40,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:35.63,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,The downflow, Plume!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:39.88,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:43.02,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,This is almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.02,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,an enormous underwater waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:56.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That's so cool!\NThe water keeps falling all the way to the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's unbelievably fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:01.39,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Very impressive, nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:06.43,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,What a massive current!\NI wonder how many hundred meters across it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:11.10,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Seeing it for yourself is completely different from\Nhearing stories about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.44,0:24:15.31,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see the bottom!  It's pitch black down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.31,0:24:17.12,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:21.95,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we fall at that speed,\Nwe'll crash into the ocean floor.  We'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:25.36,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Are you sure we'll be fine, riding this current?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:27.47,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.47,0:24:32.27,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The Sunny was crafted from the Treasure Tree, Adam.\NIt's the strongest ship there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.27,0:24:33.69,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.84,0:24:36.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.98,0:24:39.36,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:44.52,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,I hadn't heard that {\i1}that thing{\i0} was living down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.52,0:24:48.07,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,The demon that races through the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:50.88,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,The enemy of all humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:54.71,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Crew!  Turn around immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.71,0:24:56.46,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.46,0:24:58.35,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.35,0:25:00.04,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,There's a monster down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:07.93,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:11.59,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}The incomprehensibly gigantic monster octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.16,0:25:14.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's crushing several ships at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:18.37,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It has been preying on the ships that pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.37,0:25:21.64,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Please!  I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.64,0:25:26.46,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Turn around!  If we just wait for a few days,\NI'm sure that monster will{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:28.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Shut up!  Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.31,0:25:31.92,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I just had a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.70,0:25:34.68,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's tame him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.69,0:25:37.16,Main,Straw Hats,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.16,0:25:39.52,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you talking about, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:42.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We'll tame that octopus and make him pull our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.48,0:25:44.83,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.83,0:25:49.80,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Look closely, or even if you don't look closely, can't you see how {\i1}huge{\i0} that thing is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.80,0:25:52.20,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Man, it sure is big...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.65,0:25:58.30,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I don't know how many centuries it's been alive,\Nbut the Kraken appears in countless legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:26:01.24,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's a mythical beast!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Main,,0,0,0,,

